WEBVTT

00:11:29.089 --> 00:11:30.941
És el mite dels inadaptats.

00:11:31.763 --> 00:11:33.028
I diu així:

00:11:33.623 --> 00:11:35.878
fins i tot al moment del teu fracàs,

00:11:35.902 --> 00:11:38.480
ets bonic.

00:11:39.585 --> 00:11:40.737
Encara no saps,

00:11:40.761 --> 00:11:43.938
però tens l'abilitat de
reinventar-te

00:11:43.962 --> 00:11:45.160
sense fi.

00:11:45.184 --> 00:11:46.778
Aquesta és la teva bellesa.

00:11:47.694 --> 00:11:49.210
Pots ser un borratxo,

00:11:49.234 --> 00:11:51.583
supervivent d'abús,

00:11:51.607 --> 00:11:53.043
un ex convicte,

00:11:53.067 --> 00:11:54.565
un rodamón,

00:11:54.589 --> 00:11:57.867
pots perdre tot els teus diners
o la teva feina o el teu home

00:11:57.891 --> 00:12:00.305
o la teva dona, però el pitjor de tot,